{"tid":769535,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"舊愛新歡共冶一爐 美國兩女一男三角戀開花結果","createTime":"2018-08-06T08:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T11:25:42.000Z","uid":75969,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb58c83a5a3ff7ade79277615e224aa0fbddcd4","tid":769535,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180806/_2018080613060978971.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180806%2F_2018080613060978971.jpg&h=d24dbdad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現任和前度見面總是「分外眼紅」，但美國加洲有一位女子，竟然可以和丈夫及他的前女友共組和諧家庭！這名和青梅竹馬結婚的女子，與男方少時的舊情人開展「三角戀」，更希望一起養育孩子和組織家庭。由於互相呷醋的階段已經過去，現在相處融洽的三人，甚至紋上三角形紋身，以象徵他們的三角關係，又指大部份的家人都接受他們的奇怪關係。<br />\n<br />\n這段奇妙的三角關係始於三人情竇初開之時。現在坐享齊人之福的28歲的男子史特普(Terry Stroup)與28歲妻子布里特妮(Brittney)，以及「第三者」、27歲女子舍珀(Lindsay Schoepf)，早於中學時代結識並成為好友。先與史特普談戀愛的其實是舍珀，但其後二人分手，史特普便與現任妻子布里特妮墮入了愛河，雙方交往數年後便共諧連理。<br />\n<br />\n舍珀於2011年因為時任男友而搬到亞利桑那州，2016年舍珀搬回加州，便與史特普夫婦同住共享居所，結果他們「擋不住感情來襲」，自始便開展了「三人遊」。看似美滿的三人，起初亦經歷過「磨合期」，指三方曾互相呷醋的舍珀，「真正處理呷醋的唯一方法是繼續向前。我們會坐下談論，嘗試找最好方法解決。在現時來說，呷醋基本不是問題。我們知道大家的立場」。<br />\n<br />\n舍珀又指這段三角關係美滿，「我們彼此相愛，因為我們為這段關係帶來了不同的東西。人類有能力去多愛，現在我們在一起，若只能在同一時間中對一個人有這樣的感覺，會令人窒息」。<br />\n<br />\n這段「三人遊」已維持兩年，史特普夫婦於去年10月結婚一周年時，決定向舍珀「求婚」，計劃數年後舉行承諾儀式。三人又指曾經談過養育小孩，又指見過許多三角戀成功組織家庭的例子，更形容這段關係「非常美麗」。「我們有時間一起，我們各人間有不同關係。這是始於我們三個人之間的愛，永遠也是。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180806/_2018080613061038470.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180806%2F_2018080613061038470.jpg&h=f285e662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180806/_2018080613061188877.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180806%2F_2018080613061188877.jpg&h=4e78727e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180806/_2018080613061242776.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180806%2F_2018080613061242776.jpg&h=29b650a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/784009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F784009&d=1rt2mGOf%2BUhkdsep%2Bp%2FSybZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=8d74b573\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F784009&h=4e7cf154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/784009</a><br />\n<br />\n雙加大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9249a4df3e08c2d7839dbc1b25abcd53ae550a09","tid":769535,"uid":132587,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:58:15.000Z","msg":"鄧兆尊笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43dccaa29ee1e9201909ea40eb0c30ebfed403d0","tid":769535,"uid":63588,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T09:07:03.000Z","msg":"一個已經有d呼吸困難 兩個真係有窒息感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6025a5bc5a4b312bdf3bd62cfba212ae0caef957","tid":769535,"uid":29167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9249a4df3e08c2d7839dbc1b25abcd53ae550a09","tid":769535,"uid":132587,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T08:58:15.000Z","msg":"鄧兆尊笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T09:07:47.000Z","msg":"呢個真係偉人"},{"pid":"86dc27f7f9ffdfb2dba7fededb7a3eca88f15a10","tid":769535,"uid":2567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"佢張床係咩牌子？"},{"pid":"946fb5aa8569bd5738dbc577548